**AWS CLI Interaction to S3**
**——————————————**
- To list all the available buckets you can use : **aws s3 ls**
- To create a new bucket : **aws s3 mb s3://bucket-name**
- To delete the bucket : **aws s3 rb s3://bucket-name**
- To delete the bucket including files : **aws s3 rb s3://bucket-name -force**
- To set permissions while copying the files : **aws s3 cp /Users/Chitti.t/file s3://bucket-name —recursive —acl public-read**
- To copy files from local to S3 bucket : **aws s3 cp local-path s3://bucket-name**
